priateness and effectiveness of the proposed methods is\ndemonstrated using comparisons with the established non-linear procedures from\ncommercial finite element software ABAQUS and experiments with very large\ndeformations. To demonstrate the translational benefits of MTLED we also\npresent a realistic brain-shift computation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 07:37:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 04:45:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-14"}
