 fibre was able to optimize\nEIT for myelinated fibres and explain the biophysical basis of the measured\nsignals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 14:27:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-17"}
